reviewText: Awesome - I've played this for several friends and we always enjoy it.
The dvd, An Evening With Mark Gungor, was in great condition. It came in a timely manner. It also is full of very useful information.

This video is great for any couple to watch together.  This guy really understands the differences between men and women and speaks real truth.  Plus - it's hilarious!  Fall off the couch funny...well worth it!
